name: Reverse Three iCo
description:
Hello! I am not a model maker, I am not the original creator of the models in this merge. I am only someone who weighted merged these two models together and sharing it.
This Model is NSFW biased.

This model is a merge of the "three" model by discord member Dr. Derp, and the iCoMixV2 found here:
https://civitai.com/models/16164/icomix

It was merge block weighted with RSmoothStep2, with "three" as Model A, hence the name Revese-Three-iCo.

Dr. Derp recommends aspect ratio 512x704 or similar. As far as I know, no VAE is needed, HOWEVER, the use of SD-VAE, or Anything-VAE is likely good due to iCo using Anything and SD-VAE being generally good.

SD VAE:
https://huggingface.co/stabilityai/sd-vae-ft-mse
Anything VAE:
https://huggingface.co/andite/anything-v4.0/blob/main/anything-v4.0.vae.pt
The sample images we generated using the Bad Prompt V2 embedding at a .50 weight (ex: bad_prompt_v2:0.50)
found here:
https://huggingface.co/datasets/Nerfgun3/bad_prompt/blob/main/bad_prompt_version2.pt

And ControlNet found in WebUI Extensions, I can't speak to other methods.

Here's my DeviantArt page where I post SFW and NSFW content:
https://www.deviantart.com/adellanuki
